title: Was Rip Okasio Cortez Twitt that Huda Mutana was a hero?
subtitle: The definition of the hero by the Alexandrian Congresswoman Okasio Cortez should not be collected from ironic accounts.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: The Alexandrian Republic of Okasio-Cortez Twittered that Huda Mutana was more of a hero than the veterans in the United States.
